ax attacks|publisher=BBC|work=[[Newsnight]]|date=14 March 2002|access-date=16 March 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090407000929/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/programmes/newsnight/archive/1873368.stm|archive-date=7 April 2009|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* [[Sergei Popov (bioweaponeer)|Sergei Popov]]<ref>[https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/nova/bioterror/biow_popov.html \"Interviews With Biowarriors: Sergei Popov\"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170618153502/http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/nova/bioterror/biow_popov.html |date=18 June 2017 }}, (2001) ''[[Nova (American TV series)|NOVA Online]]''.</ref>\n*[[Theodor Rosebury]]\n*[[Rihab Rashid Taha]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/3021981.stm|title=US welcomes 'Dr Germ' capture|date=13 May 2003|access-date=8 March 2010|publisher=BBC|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061019042857/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/3021981.stm|archive-date=19 October 2006|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n*[[Prince Tsuneyoshi Takeda]]\n*[[Huda Salih Mahdi Ammash]]\n*[[Nassir al-Hindawi]]\n*[[Erich Traub]]<ref>{{cite book| first1 = Peter J | last1 = Jackson | first2 = Jennifer | last2 = Siegel | name-list-format = vanc |title=Intelligence and Statecraft: The Use and Limits of Intelligence in International Society|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=I3Q3_Ww-5SMC&pg=PA194|year=2005|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-275-97295-0|page=194}}</ref>\n*[[Auguste Trillat]]\n*[[Baron Otto von Rosen]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://anthrax1916.weebly.com|title=Jamie Bisher, \"Baron von Rosen's 1916 Anthrax Mission,\" 2014|work=Baron von Rosen's 1916 Anthrax Mission|access-date=24 October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413125850/http://anthrax1916.weebly.com/|archive-date=13 April 2014|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n*[[Yujiro Wakamatsu]]\n*[[Yazid Sufaat]]<ref name=\"gsAnthrax\">[http://www.globalsecurity.org/security/profiles/yazid_sufaat_works_