ji koronaviruso atvejai, prane\u0161ama apie 6 pasveikusius I\u0161 viso \u2013 491 atvejai |publisher=Lrytas.lt |date= |accessdate=2020-03-30}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|HUN}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Hungary|Hungary]]\n|525\n|20\n|40\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=T\u00e1j\u00e9koztat\u00f3 oldal a koronav\u00edrusr\u00f3l|url=https://koronavirus.gov.hu/|publisher=Cabinet Office of the Prime Minister|language=hu|date=25 March 2020|access-date=25 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BIH}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n|457\n|13\n|19\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BUL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Bulgaria|Bulgaria]]\n|485\n|14\n|30\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mh.government.bg/bg/informaciya-za-grazhdani/potvrdeni-sluchai-na-koronavirus-na-teritoriyata-na-r-blgariya/|title=\u041f\u043e\u0442\u0432\u044a\u0440\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0438 \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0438 \u043d\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441 COVID-19 \u0432 \u0411\u044a\u043b\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0438\u044f|last=|first=|date=1 Apr 2020|website=mh.government.bg|language=Bulgarian|trans-title=Confirmed COVID-19 cases in Bulgaria|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=1 Apr 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|LVA}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Latvia|Latvia]]\n|446\n|0\n|1\n|<ref>{{cite web|author=SPKC.gov.lv (Verified account) |url=https://twitter.com/SPKCentrs/status/1244624229552848896/photo/1 |title=SPKC.gov.lv on Twitter: \"Inform\u0101cija par COVID-19 saslim\u0161anas gad\u012bjumiem Latvij\u0101 |publisher=Twitter.com |date= |accessdate=2020-03-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=SPKC.gov.lvVerified account |url=https://twitter.com/SPKCentrs |title=SPKC.gov.lv (@SPKCentrs) |publisher=Twitter |date= |accessdate=2020-03-30}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|MDA}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Moldova|Moldova]]\n|423\n|5\n|23\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|SVK}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Slovakia|Slovakia]]\n|400\n|1\n|7\n|\