et-4-july-this-happened-and-then-all| title=At 9:30pm ET, 4 July, this happened|website=LESSIG Blog, v2|last=Lessig|first=Lawrence|date=4 July 2014|accessdate=23 August 2016}}</ref> After the crowdfunding deadline, Mayday PAC raised an additional $4M from large donors.\nAs of May 22, 2016, Mayday PAC is the largest crowdfunding campaign for non-profit purposes.{{citation needed|date=August 2016}} \n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |52\n|Lucyd\n|Blockchain, Wearables\n|Ethereum\n|Feb 28, 2019\n|$6m\n|$6,100,000<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tekcapital.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Lucyd-tek-RNS-3.pdf|title=Press release on Lucyd crowdfund}}</ref>\n|Community-driven augmented reality project. Has since launched an eshop for advanced eyewear. Developing blockchain apps for augmented reality. \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |53\n| [[Fidget Cube]]\n| Other\n| [[Kickstarter]]\n| {{Dts|abbr=on|2016|10|19}}<ref name=\"kickstarter-fidget-cube\"/>\n| $15K<ref name=\"kickstarter-fidget-cube\"/>\n| {{yes|$6,038,945|align=left}}<ref name=\"kickstarter-fidget-cube\">{{cite web|title=Fidget Cube: A Vinyl Desk Toy|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/antsylabs/fidget-cube-a-vinyl-desk-toy|website=Kickstarter|accessdate=15 October 2016}}</ref>\n| A desk toy designed to help users focus.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kuchera|first1=Ben|title=Fidgeted made this toy one of Kickstarter's most successful campaigns|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/9/12/12887894/fidget-cube-kickstarter-success|website=Polygon|accessdate=2016-09-13}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |54\n| ''[[Veronica Mars (film)|Veronica Mars]]''\n| [[Movie]]\n| [[Kickstarter]]\n| {{Dts|abbr=on|2013|04|13}}\n| $2M\n| {{yes|$5,702,153|align=left}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303636404579397322240026950?mg=reno64-wsj&url=http%3A%2F%2Fonline.wsj.com%2Farticle%2FSB10001424052702303636404579397322240026950.html |title='Veronica Mars' to Break the Mold for Movie Releases |